V prípade prepísania 3 znakov od pozície 10 znakmy "A" nám stačí posunuť kurzor po 9. bajt, vytvoriť 3bajtový buffer, do toho pridať "AAA" a následne to napísať do infile pomocou write.

patri@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU MINGW64 ~/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/11 (main)
$ cat infile
this is the infile's content without any uppercase letters

patri@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU MINGW64 ~/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/11 (main)
$ ./11.exe

patri@DESKTOP-I4LLMQU MINGW64 ~/Documents/OS/OS-domace/T02/os2022-sr0910-usr/T02/11 (main)
$ cat infile
this is tAAAinfile's content without any uppercase letters